OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,FThe government has promised to "crack
OL,8,Fdown" on care companies that ban
OL,9,Ffamilies from visiting their
OL,10,Fvulnerable relatives, following an ITV
OL,11,FNews investigation.
OL,13,FCare Minister Stephen Kinnock told ITV
OL,14,FNews families will "no longer be cut
OL,15,Foff from their loved ones" and
OL,16,Fpromised to improve visitation rights
OL,17,Fand end blanket bans on contact.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@EO]vD@TOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,FIt follows an ITV News investigation
OL,8,Fwhich found hundreds of families
OL,9,Fclaiming they have been restricted or
OL,10,Fbanned by care companies and councils
OL,11,Ffrom seeing loved ones with learning
OL,12,Fdisabilities, after complaining about
OL,13,Fthe quality of care.
OL,15,FStephen Kinnock told ITV News last
OL,16,Fmonth that the practice was
OL,17,F"completely unacceptable" and has now
OL,18,Fannounced a crackdown on bans and
OL,19,Frestrictions.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"We saw that in some cases, there were
OL,8,Fsettings where the family, the loved
OL,9,Fones, who had the absolute right to
OL,10,Fcome and visit, were being prevented
OL,11,Ffrom doing so. So we need to fix that,
OL,12,F" the care minister told ITV News.
OL,14,F"ITV's reporting has strengthened that
OL,15,Fview and made it clear in some of the
OL,16,Fheartbreaking cases that you
OL,17,Fidentified, that best practise was not
OL,18,Falways being followed."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,FLast month, ITV News spoke to 50
OL,8,Ffamilies who said they have had their
OL,9,Fcontact restricted with relatives with
OL,10,Flearning disabilities. Now, more than
OL,11,F200 families have come forward.
OL,13,FLawyers and disability charities told
OL,14,Fus they are seeing the use of so-
OL,15,Fcalled "contact restrictions"
OL,16,Fincreasing, as more councils struggle
OL,17,Fto find alternative care for people
OL,18,Fwith learning disabilities whose
OL,19,Ffamilies complain, and so side with
OL,20,Fcare providers to avoid care places
OL,21,Fbeing withdrawn.
OL,26,@wD@HOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,FFamilies are also unable to speak out
OL,8,Fpublicly about the restrictions due to
OL,9,Fcourt orders preventing their
OL,10,Fvulnerable relatives from being
OL,11,Fidentified. Those not subject to court-
OL,12,Fapproved rules say they fear
OL,13,F"punishment" by care providers if they
OL,14,Fdo.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"It's unacceptable, if there are
OL,8,Fvisiting rights being limited without
OL,9,Fa very clear and an exceptional basis
OL,10,Fagainst a very high bar, we will crack
OL,11,Fdown on that. The Care Quality
OL,12,FCommission really has this very
OL,13,Fclearly on their priority list to
OL,14,Fensure that they're going into those
OL,15,Fcare homes and enforcing the
OL,16,Fregulations.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"Regulation 9A is very clear that
OL,8,Fthese rights are there and that needs
OL,9,Fto be enforced. I think there's been
OL,10,Fclearly a failure to protect these
OL,11,Fvisiting rights in a relatively small
OL,12,Fbut not at all negligible number of
OL,13,Fcare homes, hospices and hospitals.
OL,14,FAnd that is what we need to crack down
OL,15,Fon.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"We are putting out guidance, very
OL,8,Fclear signals to the system to ensure
OL,9,Fthat they're clear of what does
OL,10,Fconstitute exceptional reasons for not
OL,11,Fallowing those visiting rights. And
OL,12,Fit's that clarity that I think the
OL,13,Fsystem needs."
OL,15,FIf you or anyone you know has been
OL,16,Fimpacted by this story, you can
OL,17,Fcontact us at investigations@itv.com
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,FKinnock also told ITV News the
OL,8,Fgovernment is considering changing the
OL,9,Flaw to strengthen visiting rights and
OL,10,Fstop care companies from imposing bans.
OL,12,F"We're exploring the possibility of a
OL,13,Fchange to the legislation," he told
OL,14,FITV News.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"We haven't come to a conclusion on
OL,8,Fthat yet because you always have to be
OL,9,Fa little bit careful with legislation
OL,10,Fso that you don't have unintended
OL,11,Fconsequences. This new set of guidance
OL,12,Fis a really important stepping stone
OL,13,Fon the journey to ensuring that there
OL,14,Fis consistency right across the
OL,15,Fcountry in every single care home,
OL,16,Fhospital and hospice."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,FRita came forward to ITV News after
OL,8,Fcontact with her son was dramatically
OL,9,Frestricted following multiple
OL,10,Fcomplaints she raised about his safety
OL,11,Fat a private care home funded by the
OL,12,Flocal council.
OL,14,FHer adult son has severe learning
OL,15,Fdisabilities and is under the Court of
OL,16,FProtection, which means he does not
OL,17,Fhave the mental capacity to make
OL,18,Fdecisions about his own welfare. It
OL,19,Falso means we cannot identify him or
OL,20,Fhis mum, whose name we have changed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,FRita raised her son at home for his
OL,8,Fentire childhood, with some help from
OL,9,Fcarers. When he turned 18, the local
OL,10,Fcouncil decided he would be better off
OL,11,Fbeing cared for in supported living
OL,12,Fwith full-time carers, against his
OL,13,Fmum's wishes.
OL,15,FThe moment he arrived at the home run
OL,16,Fby a private care company, Rita raised
OL,17,Fbasic safety issues. The more concerns
OL,18,Fshe raised, the more restrictions were
OL,19,Fintroduced, approved by the Court of
OL,20,FProtection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"They just put more and more
OL,8,Frestrictions on me visiting. They just
OL,9,Ftightly kept to this three times a
OL,10,Fweek for an hour. Even down to the
OL,11,Fminute. At 59 minutes, they'd be
OL,12,Ftelling me, 'your time is up, you've
OL,13,Fgot to go.' That was regardless of
OL,14,Fwhether my son was clearly enjoying my
OL,15,Fpresence there," she said.
OL,17,F"It was cruel."
OL,19,FThen Rita says she began to see signs
OL,20,Fof clear neglect.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"My son was appearing with visible
OL,8,Finjuries. He had lost a lot of weight.
OL,9,FHe was very malnourished,
OL,10,Fundernourished. He was self-harming
OL,11,Fdaily."
OL,13,FDespite raising complaints over
OL,14,Fseveral months, it was only when a
OL,15,Fsocial worker raised concerns about
OL,16,FRita's son's welfare that he was moved
OL,17,Fout of the care home and placed
OL,18,Felsewhere.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,FJacqui Shurlock, CEO of the
OL,8,FChallenging Behaviour Foundation, told
OL,9,FITV News that though any change is
OL,10,Fwelcome, there are still major
OL,11,Fsystemic issues that need to be
OL,12,Faddressed:
OL,14,FReacting to news that the government
OL,15,Fwill strengthen visiting rights and
OL,16,Finvolve families more in care
OL,17,Fdecisions, Rita said the changes are
OL,18,F"overdue".
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"This is potentially a life or death
OL,8,Fchange for many people. We desperately
OL,9,Fneed it, and all our vulnerable people
OL,10,Fneed it. They need to have family
OL,11,Fvisiting them. Family who are seeing
OL,12,Fwhat's going on. Family that are
OL,13,Fempowered to ensure that they have
OL,14,Fsafe care.
OL,16,F"We should never be excluded as a
OL,17,Fpunishment for criticising or
OL,18,Fcomplaining, this is just completely
OL,19,Foverriding human rights.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"My son was neglected, as well as
OL,8,Fbeing in danger. As well as getting
OL,9,Fincreasingly distressed, he also got
OL,10,Fthinner and thinner and thinner, and
OL,11,Fself-harming.
OL,13,F"And they just kept me shut out and
OL,14,Fcut me off from him."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,FWhen asked by ITV News whether the
OL,8,Fgovernment would be looking at reforms
OL,9,Fto the Court of Protection to stop
OL,10,Ffamilies being legally blocked from
OL,11,Fseeing their loved ones, the care
OL,12,Fminister said courts should always be
OL,13,Fan "absolute last resort".
OL,15,F"Prevention is better than cure. What
OL,16,Fwe want to be doing is getting that
OL,17,Fupstream intervention so that
OL,18,Feverybody's clear from the word go
OL,19,Fwhat their rights are," Kinnock said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"What I sincerely hope is that it'll
OL,8,Fnever need to get to a court anymore
OL,9,Fbecause everybody's going to be clear
OL,10,Ffrom the outset what their rights are.
OL,11,FI feel that if it's got to the level
OL,12,Fof getting to the court, then the
OL,13,Fsystem is failing. So we need to make
OL,14,Fsure that doesn't happen."
OL,16,FThe charity Challenging Behaviour
OL,17,FFoundation, which campaigns for people
OL,18,Fwith learning disabilities, welcomed
OL,19,Fthe government's ambitions, but argues
OL,20,Fministers must go further.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31220
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"Strengthened visiting rights and the
OL,8,Frecognition that cultural change is
OL,9,Fneeded are a start, but we are
OL,10,Fseriously concerned that the changes
OL,11,Fproposed will not go far enough as
OL,12,Fthey fail to address the underlying
OL,13,Fsystemic issues that ITV highlighted
OL,14,Fin their investigation," said Chief
OL,15,FExecutive Jacqui Shurlock.
