OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"Local authorities and the Court of
OL,8,FProtection are under pressure to
OL,9,Fmaintain existing adult social care
OL,10,Fplacements because there are not
OL,11,Fenough alternative community options.
OL,12,FWhat we need is for the Government to
OL,13,Fpublish their promised roadmap,
OL,14,Fsetting out how they will ensure that
OL,15,Fhigh quality community support is
OL,16,Fdeveloped, so that local authorities
OL,17,Fand the Court have more options to
OL,18,Fconsider.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/23
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
