OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773806609
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"At present, the focus is on stopping
OL,8,Fproviders from withdrawing support
OL,9,Frather than the right of a person to
OL,10,Fhave a family life, due to a dearth of
OL,11,Fplacements."
OL,13,FJon Sparkes OBE, chief executive of
OL,14,Flearning disability charity Mencap,
OL,15,Fsaid: "Strengthening visiting rights
OL,16,Fis a welcome step, and it's appalling
OL,17,Fthe Government must mandate the
OL,18,Ffundamental right for family members
OL,19,Fto see each other.
OL,26,@sD@LO]wD@GOU
