OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'crackdown' on
OL,4,Cfamilies being cut off from disabled
OL,5,Crelatives
OL,7,F"This issue was highlighted during the
OL,8,Fpandemic. As we look to the Covid
OL,9,FInquiry's Module 3 report on Thursday,
OL,10,Fwe expect a clear acknowledgement of
OL,11,Fthese and many other failings towards
OL,12,Fpeople with a learning disability. No
OL,13,Fone should ever again be isolated from
OL,14,Fthe people they love."
